https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1z2Du9BEWrWu5fx14sGhlNJstrE.jpg A few months after Ina left the position as the President of the Philippines, she is back in the media limelight as she releases a book of her life in her journey as a mother to her children and as a mother to the people of the Philippines. Ina now lives a simple life with her beloved children, together with her long-time best friend, Rowena. Ang Tanging Ina Mo: Last na 'to!
